I finally gave in & tried the @maybelline_ind superstay vinyl ink liquid lipsticks.
It is very pigmented and it will take you a while to apply it carefully & neatly. It makes my lips look fuller & oh so beautifully glossy. 

Coming to if it is transfer proof or not. It does transfer when I kiss the back of my hands or when I drink water. But hold on, even after the transfer the shine & the pigment doesn't lighten as you would expect. The look & gloss remains intact. I had quite a heavy & cheesy paneer roll for dinner that day & to my surprise the lipstick was still looking great at the end of the day. I was expecting the shine to go away completely but it didn't.
HAVE YOU TRIED IT YET??🤤
